      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Envoy Improvisation</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl17_LabelName\">When an ally within 60 feet must succeed at a Reflex save to avoid a harmful effect, as a reaction before your ally attempts the saving throw, you can grant the ally a +2 bonus to that saving throw.<br><br>At 6th level, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to have the ally roll twice on the saving throw and take the better result. Both of those rolls benefit from the +2 bonus provided by this ability.</span></p>",
